# GitHub Actions Secrets (must be set in repository settings)

YC_CLOUD_ID=your_yandex_cloud_id
YC_FOLDER_ID=your_yandex_folder_id
YC_SA_JSON_CREDENTIALS=your_base64_encoded_service_account_json
KUBECONFIG=your_base64_encoded_kubeconfig
REGISTRY_USERNAME=your_container_registry_username
REGISTRY_PASSWORD=your_container_registry_password

# How to add secrets to GitHub

1. Go to repository Settings
2. Navigate to Secrets and variables > Actions
3. Click 'New repository secret' and add each variable above
